author: lhazlewood
msg: - Finished initial change to configuration infrastructure to use the new IniShiroFilter and supporting classes.  The existing ShiroFilter class and all of its supporting *Resource and *Configurtion classes still exist and have not been changed, but they are now deprecated in favor of the new AbstractShiroFilter and IniShiroFilter mechanisms.
- Updated the sample web application's web.xml to use the new IniShiroFilter.
- Added or modified unit tests for 99-100% line coverage for IniShiroFilter, IniFilterChainResolverFactory, DefaultFilterChainManager, and PathMatchingFilterChainResolver.
